.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/feature-catalog/governance/feature-flag-governance.md:52:- `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/lib/config/capability-flags.ts` - Memory roadmap phase and flag governance, including `scope-governance` fallback and intentionally default-off dormant flags such as adaptive ranking.
