.opencode/skills/system-code-graph/feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md:304:Opt-in `CALLS` edge write-path differentiation (`SPECKIT_CODE_GRAPH_EDGE_CONFIDENCE_DIFFERENTIATION`, default off) that replaces the legacy uniform `0.8/INFERRED/heuristic` tier with resolution-specific confidence and evidence class for same-file and cross-file call resolution.
