.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md:476:Delete and retention paths now have default-off tombstone infrastructure behind `SPECKIT_SOFT_DELETE_TOMBSTONES`. The default remains hard deletion, while the opt-in path preserves the first `deleted_at` timestamp and lets retention sweeps target purgeable tombstoned rows.
