.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md:1271:Mixed ID formats (`42`, `"42"`, `mem:42`) caused deduplication failures in hybrid search. Normalization was applied in `combinedLexicalSearch()` for the new pipeline and in legacy `hybridSearch()` for the dedup map. Regression tests `T031-LEX-05` and `T031-BASIC-04` verify the fix.
