.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md:3112:Direct-run Node script at `mcp-server/scripts/repair-graph-metadata.mjs` normalizes graph-metadata.json to the v1 schema, maps legacy `importance_tier: "high"` to `important`, compacts archived metadata that fails V-rule V8, and realigns stale `memory_lineage.logical_key` rows with current `memory_index` identities. Direct-run, idempotent on re-run, writes `/tmp/repair-graph-metadata-*` backups before any real mutation.
