.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md:3180:**Current update:** The legacy `postSearchPipeline` path was removed entirely, leaving the 4-stage pipeline as the only code path. A shared `resolveEffectiveScore()` function in `pipeline/types.ts` replaced both Stage 2's `resolveBaseScore()` and Stage 3's local `effectiveScore()`, ensuring a consistent fallback chain (`intentAdjustedScore -> rrfScore -> score -> similarity/100`, all clamped [0,1]) across all stages.
