.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md:3665:### Daemon ownership re-election (default-on)
.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md:3669:The shared daemon used to die with its owner because the owner killed it on shutdown. Re-election lets the daemon outlive its owner so secondary sessions keep the backend. It is still default-on, but the launcher code is now the source of that default; runtime configs no longer set `SPECKIT_DAEMON_REELECTION`.
