.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/checklist.md:38:- [ ] CHK-003 [P1] The directive block is approved against all seven existing hubs.
