   442	## 10. GOVERNANCE AND SCOPE
   443	
   444	| Variable | Default | Type | Description | Source |
   445	|----------|---------|------|-------------|--------|
   446	| `SPECKIT_MEMORY_ROADMAP_PHASE` | `scope-governance` | string | Active memory roadmap phase: `baseline`, `lineage`, `graph`, `adaptive`, `scope-governance`. | `lib/config/capability-flags.ts` |
   447	| `SPECKIT_MEMORY_LINEAGE_STATE` | `true` | boolean | Lineage state tracking capability. Graduated ON. | `lib/config/capability-flags.ts` |
   448	| `SPECKIT_MEMORY_GRAPH_UNIFIED` | `true` | boolean | Graph unified capability for roadmap tracking. Graduated ON. | `lib/config/capability-flags.ts` |
